data.description: Charming 2-story townhome - previously remodeled! Most recent updates include new Pex piping from water heater to 1st floor, fresh neutral paint downstairs, refreshed bathrooms, and epoxy flooring in the garage! Inside, you'll also find tile flooring throughout the 1st floor, a soaring ceiling in the living room, and the lovely eat-in kitchen boasting Quartz countertops and a tile backsplash! Also downstairs is the half bath with washer/dryer connections while upstairs holds the 2 carpeted bedrooms and freshly painted full bath. The backyard offers a patio and artificial turf for easy maintenance. Located on an "offset" end unit for minimum connection to next door unit! Easy access to shopping and dining off I-69 less than a mile away, plus proximity to Bush Airport, Beltway 8, and I-610!
